author: Dailymail.Com Reporter
title: Fox host attacks 'jealous women' criticizing Ivanka Trump | Daily Mail Online
text: Judge Jeanine Pirro slams 'loud classless' women marchers for forcing Nordstrom to drop Ivanka's clothing line - when the president's daughter 'epitomizes everything they claim to champion' The Fox News host launched into a passionate tirade on her show Saturday night Pirro, who has previously said she is a friend of Trump's, attacked Ivanka's critics 'You will not defeat this woman, and you will not set us back,' the Fox host said On Saturday Donald Trump tweeted his daughter has been a victim of the press
